{
  "stem": "11472.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say the front isn't too far, not too far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're excited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, a few weeks later, the men go out, and they find out that we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The front went through us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not hear anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're underneath.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They come back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians were here, and they left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is March, beginning of March.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, all my uncles went to a friend-- I think my father went to this friend that had the Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made up with him that he would let in a big, a long rope with a bottle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that bottle it would say that we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, we know that a front is around us, because what was happening-- the Germans were fighting forward and retreating, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the front was going on for another month in our vicinity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day they go and they find the bottle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you imagine how we felt?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We lived to see the destruction of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING] God, how we used to pray.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All we wanted was just to see-- we didn't even care if we lived or not, but Hitler should, should not be around.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But his army should perish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- and his regime should perish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was everybody's prayer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The men went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For a week they-- we still stayed in the grotto because we were afraid the front shouldn't go back and forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A week later, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they came with trucks, with Russian soldiers, trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took us out from the grotto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We came out--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
